description: This Chainlink VRF nut low Gatinho purrs with a rating of 1, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 1, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, Stringalong for East, Box for South, and Nine Lives for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/50011-57492-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [1 Vote, Nut Low]
